and I just… I couldn't cope with it.</i>

229
01:07:55,440 --> 01:07:57,920
<i>And I did just not wanna be here anymore.</i>

230
01:08:00,160 --> 01:08:04,040
<i>You say, "There are no words.
"I can't breathe. I can't focus."</i>

231
01:08:05,920 --> 01:08:07,960
<i>I just felt like it was all just</i>

232
01:08:09,280 --> 01:08:12,599
<i>spiraling out of control.
I just didn't know how to feel about it</i>

233
01:08:12,600 --> 01:08:14,720
<i>or what was gonna happen or what to do.</i>

234
01:08:17,320 --> 01:08:21,119
<i>Just felt that the trust and the team
