they might wanna victimize you or…</i>

239
01:08:43,760 --> 01:08:45,480
<i>point the finger towards you?</i>

240
01:08:49,520 --> 01:08:52,599
<i>It crossed my mind at times whether
they were trying to put the blame on me</i>

241
01:08:52,600 --> 01:08:54,720
