242
01:09:28,480 --> 01:09:31,440
<i>In terms of overwhelming fear and panic,</i>

243
01:09:31,960 --> 01:09:33,880
<i>what were you afraid of?</i>

244
01:09:34,400 --> 01:09:37,160
<i>That they were going to think
