245
01:09:37,680 --> 01:09:41,480
<i>Okay, and what would happen
if they thought that?</i>

246
01:09:42,560 --> 01:09:44,040
<i>That this would happen.</i>

247
01:09:44,800 --> 01:09:47,360
- <i>Right.
